body:
Captain Marvel: Ben Mendelsohn elogia la sceneggiatura definendola “finemente realizzata”

Captain Marvel si avvicina rapidamente mentre i Marvel Studios si preparano a rilasciare il suo primo film solista con protagonista principale femminile a marzo. I fan vogliono e si aspettano che il film sia grandioso dato il successo del fumetto, del personaggio, del titolo e gli standard qualitativi per il cinema di massa che hanno settato.

Nel film Mendelsohn interpreta un Skrull antagonistico…

body:
Gimme Good Climate captain marvel!


I was sick and tired of everything,

When I called you last night from London

All I do is work and dry the dishes and eat salad,

Wishing being worthy.


Gimme! Gimme! Gimme good climate!

Won’t somebody help me read all of the books!

Gimme! Gimme! Gimme good climate!

I really want to read all of the books!


captain marvel, I was defeated, you won the war.

captain marvel, promise to love me forever more.

captain marvel, couldn’t escape if I wanted to.

captain marvel, knowing my fate is to be with you.

Yeet-yeet-yeet-yeet-yeet captain marvel!

Finally facing captain marvel.


You are the dancing actor, here in London.

Dancing actor, feel the beat from the tambourine.

You can read all of the books, you can read all of the books, having the time of your life.


Gimme! Gimme! Gimme! good climate,

Won’t somebody help me read all of the books.


This random song generator is making me laugh my ass of 🤣

summary: Theory based on Disney’s upcoming movie releases
body:
Theory based on Disney’s upcoming movie releases

The Disney movies are staggered in Spring- Aladdin, Lion King, and Toy Story. (Too late for Frozen teasers)

Toy Story teasers dropped 8 months before its release date- with Ralph Breaks the Internet.

The next up on the block is Dumbo (March 29th)

And Captain Marvel (March 8th)

I’m assuming, at this point, Dumbo is a focal point for Frozen teasers.
